Ex parte: In the Matter of The Chicago Title and Trust Company, Petitioner. January 2, 1906. Mr. Joseph E. Baden and Mr. Newton Wyeth for petitioner. Mr. Henry S. Robbins, Mr: Wallace Heckman and Mr. James G. Elsdon for respondents.
